result.name: McDonald's

reviews.text: McDonald's is McDonald's. What you see is what you get and this branch in Tung Chung is always full packed with foodies. Whenever I pass by here, there's always a very long queue and you can hardly find a vacant seat esp on weekends but this is my go to place if I want to grab coffee and sandwiches real quick as their McCafe doesn't have long queue.

On a regular non-holiday Wednesday at around 9:30am, I didn't need to wait in line, and my breakfast was on the tray in front of me before I finished paying. And it was hot. Hot crispy hashbrowns, hot sandwich and hot coffee. The restaurant was 80% full, so no trouble finding a seat. A very good experience is possible at McDonald's.
Champignon Angus burger best thing on the menu

result.name: Citygate Outlets

reviews.text:
Calling City Gate an Upscale Outlet Mall sounds like an oxymoron. That's exactly what it is.
A nice mall with many shops selling last season products, however bargains though possible are hard to find.
Large areas have closed for refurbishment, good selection of shops however prices are not that cheap like most outlet shopping.
The mall was not bad.  However, the shops were mainly designer brands. And they are targeting mainland China visitors.   It can get pretty crowded in weekends.

Lots of shops...and more shops.
Taste supermarket is great...well stocked with 'international' goodies.
Lots of options for lunch or a quick snack.
You can check out cheap stuff there easily

result.name: 麥當勞

reviews.text: 叫沒有吃過這麼塌的牛角包⋯下次只點咖啡好了
沒有自助點餐機，座位很少，店員餐具(湯匙)漏給，漢堡內的生菜看起來很糟糕...
地方寬大，坐位多，重有無敵落地玻、璃，喝一口珈琲，坐窗边看街景，十分寫意。還有最要有厕所。

McDonald's is McDonald's. What you see is what you get and this branch in Tung Chung is always full packed with foodies. Whenever I pass by here, there's always a very long queue and you can hardly find a vacant seat esp on weekends but this is my go to place if I want to grab coffee and sandwiches real quick as their McCafe doesn't have long queue.
正常麥當勞食物水準，長時間多人買食物，等待時間比較長，如果中午吃飯時間，排隊要10分鐘或以上，1-2人較易搵位，3人以上要等位，或要分開坐，清楚度低
